The standardized actions are outlined below:

ACTIONS
• Move to coordinates (x, y).
• Gather resources from one or both locations: resource_x and resource_y, situated near your base at (base_x, base_y).
• Train a unit of the chosen type:
  - A Worker is an acceptable base.
  - Light, Heavy, and Ranged units can be trained in a Barracks.
• Construct a building of the specified type (building_type) at designated coordinates (x, y):
  - Your base can build either a Base or a Barracks structure.
• Launch an attack on the enemy unit positioned at (enemy_x, enemy_y).